(2, 'b857a-harry-potter.png', 'Harry Potter: De Volta a Hogwarts”: especial comemora os 20 anos da saga', '<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Lan&ccedil;ado no primeiro dia de 2022, o especial da HBO Max<strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;Harry Potter: De Volta a Hogwarts&nbsp;</strong>surge para celebrar os 20 anos de &ldquo;A Pedra Filosofal&rdquo;, primeiro filme da franquia inspirada nos<strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;livros de J. K. Rowling</strong>. Pouco mais de uma semana depois de sua estreia, o programa dirigido por Casey Patterson promove o reencontro da equipe da saga do bruxo mais famoso do cinema e j&aacute; &eacute; o produto mais assistido na plataforma de streaming em toda a Am&eacute;rica Latina.</span></span></p>\r\n<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Com uma hora e quarenta e cinco minutos de dura&ccedil;&atilde;o, a produ&ccedil;&atilde;o re&uacute;ne as estrelas da saga Daniel Radcliffe (Harry), Emma Watson (Hermione) e Rupert Grint (Rony), al&eacute;m do cineasta Chris Columbus e outros nomes do elenco. Em Harry Potter: De Volta a Hogwarts, atores e membros da equipe de produ&ccedil;&atilde;o da s&eacute;rie revelam bastidores e compartilham curiosidades, hist&oacute;rias e detalhes de suas experi&ecirc;ncias na franquia iniciada h&aacute; duas d&eacute;cadas.</span></span></p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\" font-size:=\"\" open=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); margin: 0px 0px 1em; text-align: center; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \">\r\n	<div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/pEVTnVnIYP8?feature=oembed\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; inset: 0px; width: 768px; height: 432px;\" title=\"Harry Potter: De Volta A Hogwarts | Clipe Exclusivo | HBO Max\" width=\"800\"></iframe></span></span></div>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Os encontros da equipe de Harry Potter se d&atilde;o nos cen&aacute;rios do primeiro filme, que foram remontados exclusivamente para a produ&ccedil;&atilde;o da HBO. No especial, o p&uacute;blico poder&aacute; revisitar a escola de magia Hogwarts, a cabana de Hagrid e outros lugares marcantes do primeiro filme.</span></span></p>\r\n<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Para ajudar voc&ecirc; a entrar no clima antes de assistir ao especial, n&oacute;s preparamos uma sele&ccedil;&atilde;o com os t&iacute;tulos da s&eacute;rie liter&aacute;ria criada por J. K. Rowling. Confira a lista e aproveite a leitura!</span></span></p>\r\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" font-size:=\"\" open=\"\" style=\"border-top: none; border-right: none; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(143, 152, 161); border-left: none; height: 0px; margin: 1.65em auto; border-image: initial; max-width: 100px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \" />\r\n<h3 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.estantevirtual.com.br/livros/j-k-rowling/harry-potter-e-a-pedra-filosofal/3045239662?show_suggestion=0\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; 