ong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Para ir al&eacute;m do filme&hellip;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<h3 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a aria-label=\"As Fabulosas fábulas de Iauaretê (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.estantevirtual.com.br/livros/kaka-wera-jecupe/as-fabulosas-fabulas-de-iauarete/2949102505?show_suggestion=0\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(40, 150, 170); text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">As Fabulosas F&aacute;bulas de Iauaret&ecirc;</a>, Kaka Wera Jecupe</span></span></h3>\r\n<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Acompanhadas por desenhos de Sawara, filha de 11 anos do autor,&nbsp;<strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">As fabulosas f&aacute;bulas de Iauaret&ecirc;&nbsp;</strong>falam sobre temas como medo, coragem, d&uacute;vida, amor, morte, paz e oportunidade, al&eacute;m dos erros e acertos que vivenciamos, de maneira divertida e emocionante.</span></span></p>\r\n', '<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Para os nossos leitores, preparamos uma lista com sete filmes que apresentam &agrave;s crian&ccedil;as as hist&oacute;rias de popula&ccedil;&otilde;es origin&aacute;rias do pa&iacute;s. Confira!</span></span></p>\r\n', 'quarto-post', 'Blog-Cine', '2021-09-04');
