(10, 'bf8cc-videogame.jpg', '8 filmes e séries de TV inspirados em jogos de videogame.', '<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	Desde os anos 1990, as produ&ccedil;&otilde;es audiovisuais interagem cada vez mais com os jogos de videogame, tanto inspirando o surgimento de novos games como sendo inspirada por suas narrativas. O encontro de estreia desses dois universos foi em 1993 com o lan&ccedil;amento do filme Super Mario Bros, dos diretores Rocky Morton e&nbsp;Annabel Jankel e que tornou-se conhecido como a primeira adapta&ccedil;&atilde;o de um videogame para o cinema.</p>\r\n<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	De l&aacute; para c&aacute;, as hist&oacute;rias adaptadas dos games se tornaram um sucesso no cinema e na TV e in&uacute;meros s&atilde;o os filmes e s&eacute;ries que surgem atrav&eacute;s desse di&aacute;logo. Aqui, n&oacute;s selecionamos oito dessas produ&ccedil;&otilde;es audiovisuais, dispon&iacute;veis para voc&ecirc; conferir no streaming. Confira!</p>\r\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" font-size:=\"\" open=\"\" style=\"border-top: none; border-right: none; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(143, 152, 161); border-left: none; height: 0px; margin: 1.65em auto; border-image: initial; max-width: 100px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \" />\r\n<h3 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	Assassin&rsquo;s Creed (2017), Justin Kurzel</h3>\r\n<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	Callum Lynch (Michael Fassbender) descobre que &eacute; descendente de um membro da Ordem dos Assassinos e, via mem&oacute;ria gen&eacute;tica, revive as aventuras do guerreiro Aguilar, seu ancestral espanhol do s&eacute;culo XV. Dotado de novos conhecimentos e incr&iacute;veis habilidades, ele volta aos dias de hoje pronto para enfrentar os Templ&aacute;rios.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\" font-size:=\"\" open=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); margin: 0px 0px 1em; text-align: center; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \">\r\n	<div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative;\">\r\n		<iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jTgzJ79KDsg?feature=oembed\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; inset: 0px; width: 768px; height: 432px;\" title=\"Assassin\'s Creed | Trailer Oficial | Legendado HD\" width=\"800\"></iframe></div>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	<strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Para ir al&eacute;m do filme&hellip;﻿</strong></p>\r\n<h3 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	<a aria-label=\"Assassins Creed - Renascença (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.estantevirtual.com.br/livros/oliver-bowden/assassins-creed-renascenca/617920280?show_suggestion=0&amp;busca_es=1\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(40, 150, 170); text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Assassins Creed &ndash; Renascen&ccedil;a</a>, Oliver Bowden</h3>\r\n<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	Tra&iacute;do pelas fam&iacute;lias que governam as cidades-estado italianas, Ezio embarca em uma jornada em busca de vingan&ccedil;a. Para erradicar a corrup&ccedil;&atilde;o e recuperar a honra de sua fam&iacute;lia, ele ir&aacute; aprender a Arte dos Assassinos. Ao longo do caminho, o jovem ter&aacute; de contar com a sabedoria de grandes mentores, como Leonardo da Vinci e Nicolau Maquiavel, sabendo que sua sobreviv&ecirc;ncia depende de muita habilidade.</p>\r\n<div 0px=\"\" class=\"wp-block-image\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" max-width:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	<figure class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"display: table; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); margin: 0px auto; text-align: center; clear: both;\">\r\n		<a href=\"https://www.estantevirtual.com.br/livros/oliver-bowden/assassins-creed-renascenca/617920280?show_suggestion=0&amp;busca_es=1\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(40, 150, 170); text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-52374\" sizes=\"(max-width: 199px) 100vw, 199px\" src=\"https://blog.estantevirtual.com.br/wp-content/uploads/51WJ7abFdL._SY346_-199x300.jpg\" srcset=\"https://blog.estantevirtual.com.br/wp-content/uploads/51WJ7abFdL._SY346_-199x300.jpg 199w, https://blog.estantevirtual.com.br/wp-content/uploads/51WJ7abFdL._SY346_-80x120.jpg 80w, https://blog.estantevirtual.com.br/wp-content/uploads/51WJ7abFdL._SY346_.jpg 230w\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px;\" /></a></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"su-button-center\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; text-align: center;\" text-align:=\"\" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	<a class=\"su-button su-button-style-soft\" href=\"https://www.estantevirtual.com.br/livros/oliver-bowden/assassins-creed-renascenca/617920280?show_suggestion=0&amp;busca_es=1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(60, 150, 141); font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; background-color: rgb(74, 187, 176); border-radius: 5px; text-decoration-line: none !important; display: inline-block !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\" target=\"_blank\"><span -20px=\"\" 0px=\"\" block=\"\" blog.estantevirtual.com.br=\"\" border-radius:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" content-box=\"\" display:=\"\" images=\"\" includes=\"\" plugins=\"\" shortcodes-ultimate=\"\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(129, 208, 200); font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 20px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 6px 16px; vertical-align: baseline; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; background: url(\" styles=\"\" text-shadow:=\"\" wp-content=\"\">&nbsp;Ver livros</span></a></div>\r\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" font-size:=\"\" open=\"\" style=\"border-top: none; border-right: none; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(143, 152, 161); border-left: none; height: 0px; margin: 1.65em auto; border-image: initial; max-width: 100px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \" />\r\n<h3 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	Minecraft: Story Mode (2018)</h3>\r\n<p 0px=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" margin:=\"\" open=\"\" outline:=\"\" padding:=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\">\r\n	Respo